    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273804</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、危ない……
近づかないの……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, it could be dangerous... 
Don't get too close to it...! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うぉっ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぷっは～、
びっくらこいた、
おどろいた、と</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ta-dah! Did I surprise you? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>危うくバラバラになるとこだど。
帰ったら文句言ってやんねぇと、
ぶつぶつぶつ、と…</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I thought I'd be scattered all over the place, but turned 
out to be a really nice landing. The journey was pretty rough, though. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review Translation</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんだ、おめぇら、
人のことジロジロ見て</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh! People are staring at me so infatuatedly! </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Review translation</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はっはっはぁ～ん、
このアルベルト様の格好良さに
見とれてるんだべな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehe. Do I, the great Albert, bear such 
a nice figure to be observed like this? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルベルト……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I take it your name is... Albert...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだんだ、そうだど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yep, that'd be correct. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274696</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン様のお達しで、
おめぇらのとこに来てやっただ。
感謝せぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...And since I’m such a good friend of Miss Norn I
couldn’t refuse when she asked me to come all 
the way here. Congratulations, you get to meet me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>...And since I’m such good friends with Miss Norn I
couldn’t refuse when she asked me to come all 
the way here. Congratulations, you get to meet me!
~Gator </Notes>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルンの……！？
どういうこと？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Friend of Norn...!? Could it be THAT Norn...!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～ぁ、
長旅してきたもんで、
腹減っちまっただなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah! I'm so worn out from that long trip! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふかし芋の
ひとつやふたつ、
出てこんもんか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You've made me wait outside forever. Pfft, you 
really must be country bumpkins if your manners 
are this poor.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>maybe "Pfff, you must really be country bumpkins with manners like that."  ~Gator</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃ、じゃあ……
ひとまず中に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Well I guess you can come inside
our house for the time being...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_010_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あー、そったら中行くだが。
芋だけじゃなく、
茶も出すんだど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, let's get inside, yes! Maybe you're not that much of a 
country bumpkin, after all. But don't worry—I understand how much 
you desired a tea party outside with me. </EnglishText>
      <Notes>I don't think that's quite right. May need a translator to review that.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
